item.title: Quick Multitable Export
item.description: Export all on a single page Multitables are a great way to quickly find key relationships in your data. Now it is easier than ever to take those insights away and build your data story with XLSX exports. Multitables can either be exported as a complete tab book, with a table of contents and multiple fields or measures for each table cell, or you can instantly grab an XLSX file of just what you see on screen.
